description: Theres no let-up in the action in this new issue of Batman! In the third part of Endgame, the Joker spreads his madness through Gotham City! Then, in Robin Rises, Batman and his friends return from their mission to Apokolips with Damians remains, but can he be brought back? In Batman: Eternal meanwhile, Batman tackles Gothams gang war, but the police arent impressed! And last but by no means least, we bring you the eagerly awaited final instalment of Nightwing! What happened to Dick Grayson? Find out here!

This issue, Batman faces danger from every direction! In the latest installment of Endgame, the Dark Knight has to tackle the madness the Joker has unleashed on Gotham, while using his detective skills to find answers! Then, in Robin Rises: Alpha, he and the rest of the Bat-family must face the vengeful Kalibak! Could the back-from-the-dead Damian be the key to beating him? Finally, in Batman Eternal, Batman joins with the Batman of Japan for some martial arts action!

There are some serious parenting problems in this issue of Batman! In Batman & Robin, Batman has to get used to the reborn Damian, now with superpowers. Meanwhile, in Batman Eternal Batgirl, Catwoman, Spoiler and Julia all have problems with their own fathers. Last but not least, in the second part of Friends, we learn the consequences of being friends with the Joker!

The Caped Crusader faces all manner of threats, from the Joker and his Joker-ized hordes, to gang war and police corruption, to a threat from outer space! It's 100 pages of all-out action and adventure, and we know you won't want to miss a single page of it!

Its here! The show-stopping finale of Endgame. Believe us, after this, nothing will be the same for Batman again! Then, in Batman & Robin, the Caped Crusader tries to make sense of Damians powers, while in Batman Eternal, trouble is brewing on all sides! Its 100 pages of Bat action!

Its true, theres a new Batman in town! You can find out who it is in the all-action issue of Batman! Meanwhile, with his father gone, Damian aka Robin embarks on a dangerous journey. And in the ongoing Batman Eternal, events in Gotham spiral even further out of control!

In this issue of Batman, the new Dark Knight faces his biggest challenge yet Gee Gee Heung! Meanwhile, in Robin, Son of Batman, Damian continues his Year of Blood and in Batman Eternal, Batwing faces terror under Arkham Asylum!

We have it all for you this issue, from an origin story for the deadly Mr Bloom, to a clash between Robin and Deathstroke, to a Batman and Killer Croc team-up in Batman Eternal! You wont want to miss one page of it!
